OL,3,CGraham Linehan receives settlement
OL,4,Cfrom Met over arrest for social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FGraham Linehan has been awarded a
OL,8,Fsettlement from the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice over a civil claim against the
OL,10,Fforce after he was arrested for social
OL,11,Fmedia posts about transgender issues.
OL,13,FThe Irish comedy writer was arrested
OL,14,Fby police at Heathrow Airport, after
OL,15,Fflying in from Arizona in September on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of inciting violence over
OL,17,Fthree posts he made on the social
OL,18,Fmedia platform X.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
