OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783639110
OL,3,CGraham Linehan receives settlement
OL,4,Cfrom Met over arrest for social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FThe 58-year-old announced in October
OL,8,Fthat the investigation into his posts
OL,9,Fhad been dropped but said he intended
OL,10,Fto "hold the police accountable".
OL,12,FIt is understood that a settlement has
OL,13,Fbeen reached in a civil claim, and
OL,14,Ffour officers have received learning
OL,15,Fthrough reflection, a non-disciplinary
OL,16,Fprocess to resolve low-level
OL,17,Fperformance issues.
OL,19,FAccording to reports, Linehan received
OL,20,F#25,000 in the settlement.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@`O]
