OL,3,CGraham Linehan receives settlement
OL,4,Cfrom Met over arrest for social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Met said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise the considerable distress
OL,9,Fcaused to Mr Linehan, and have offered
OL,10,Four sincere apologies.
OL,12,F"This case prompted a significant
OL,13,Fchange, which means the Met no longer
OL,14,Finvestigates non-crime hate incidents.
OL,16,F"We believe this will provide clearer
OL,17,Fdirection for officers, reduce
OL,18,Fambiguity and enable them to focus on
OL,19,Fmatters that meet the threshold for
OL,20,Fcriminal investigations."
OL,26,@oD@bOUtD@AOU|D@YO]
