OL,3,CGraham Linehan receives settlement
OL,4,Cfrom Met over arrest for social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FHe was cleared of harassing
OL,8,Ftransgender campaigner Sophia Brooks
OL,9,Fwith a series of social media posts
OL,10,Fbefore and after an incident outside
OL,11,Fthe Battle Of Ideas conference in
OL,12,FWestminster on October 19, 2024.
OL,14,FHe posted on X at the time he was
OL,15,Fcleared: "With the aid of the Free
OL,16,FSpeech Union, I still aim to hold the
OL,17,Fpolice accountable for what is only
OL,18,Fthe latest attempt to silence and
OL,19,Fsuppress gender-critical voices on
OL,20,Fbehalf of dangerous and disturbed men."
